title: A Child Is Pulled Alive From the Rubble in Syria
text:
A Child Is Pulled Alive From the Rubble in Syria 2/21/2017 4:25AM A young girl was pulled alive from the rubble on Sunday after Syrian government forces bombed the opposition-held Damascus suburb of Tishreen. The video was released on Tuesday by Syrian Civil Defense, a group of volunteers from local communities. Photo:Syrian Civil Defense Transcript
